@baseUrl = http://localhost:5275
@movieId = 1

### App metadata
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Version
GET {{baseUrl}}/version

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### List movies
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies

### Get a movie by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies/{{movieId}}

### Create a movie
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Matrix",
  "releaseYear": 1999,
  "genre": "Science Fiction",
  "director": "Lana Wachowski and Lilly Wachowski"
}

### OpenAPI document
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json

### Scalar API docs
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs
